  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduo a libxfce4util</title>

    <para>
      The <application>libxfce4util</application> package is a basic utility
library for the <application>Xfce</application> desktop environment.
    </para>

    &lfs113_checked;

    <bridgehead renderas="sect3">Informao do Pacote</bridgehead>
    <itemizedlist spacing="compact">
      <listitem>
        <para>
          Transferncia (HTTP): <ulink url="&libxfce4util-download-http;"/>
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>
